description: This roaming rotisserie is home to the most tasty roasted potatoes and farm-fresh sweet corn to ever hit the streets. This culinary crew concocts their own compound butters and custom blended salts from locally sourced ingredients, which perfectly complement their incredible selection of delectable corn and potatoes stuffed to perfection.So come out to Eyes & Ears because their luscious lovely local grub will keep you grinning from ear to ear, all year round.
name: Eyes & Ears Corn Roasters
